<L>__{interior kitchenette few minutes later}
<A>__{everyone sits at the kitchen table. bobby is dressed for school, arthur is changed. ben sets up a laptop computer.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{as you know, i represent the estate of your uncle cyrus kriticos.}
